      "cooked": "<p>meqe ky eshte kendi shkrimeve te shkrimtarevr, po vendos kete</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://peizazhe.com/2019/12/24/urimet-e-zotit-shyti/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/9/8/98f16b4d32e6fa886df96ae5f10bc9b2b8e295df.jpeg\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://peizazhe.com/2019/12/24/urimet-e-zotit-shyti/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"04:02AM - 24 December 2019\">Peizazhe të fjalës – 24 Dec 19</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:600/385;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/f/6/f60eb86052c005cd9a7186294e86f55772af9299.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"600\" height=\"385\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://peizazhe.com/2019/12/24/urimet-e-zotit-shyti/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">URIMET E ZOTIT SHYTI</a></h3>\n\n  <p>(Më poshtë, disa pak urime dhe kujtime, për të gjithë ata që e nisin edhe ditën e Krishtlindjes me një espresso)  Z. SHYTI PËR MBINGARKESËN E KALEND</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
