      "cooked": "<p>Shqiperi o meme e mjere<br>\ns’te kuptova asnjehere<br>\nI modhi <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
