      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/x/13edae/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2019-12-27T20:47:44.499Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ne parliament mes zhurmes<br>\nHyri nje mize<br>\nPikerisht kur po flitej<br>\nPer te tmerrshmen krize<br>\nFilloi te fluturonte pa pyetur kerkend<br>\nKu I donte qejfi shkonte zinte vend<br>\nParlamenti mbare u bezdis aq shume<br>\nSa te gjithe pas mizes vershuan si lume<br>\nArriten ta kapin , dhe harrusn krizen<br>\nFilluan diskutimet ne lidhje me mizen</p>",
