      "created_at": "2019-12-29T19:05:07.213Z",
      "cooked": "<p>xha tani shihe kete faqe interneti, flet per testimin e shikimit nga vete personi. Harta e shkronjave ne faqe do shkarkuar e printuar, ne nje flete A4 te bardhe dhe te jesh 3.05m larg kur te besh testin.  Duhet te jesh vet i 2te qe te behet kontrolli i saktesise tende.<br>\nme pak anglisht dhe matematike mund ti kuptosh udhezimet dhe te gjesh numrin tend te syzeve.</p>\n<p>Harta e shkronjave dhe udhezimet: <a href=\"https://visionsource.com/patients/free-eye-chart-download/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Free Eye Chart - Download, Print, Test | Vision Source</a></p>\n<p>tabela e gjetjes se nr. te syrit: <a href=\"https://www.happyeyesight.com/get-20-20-vision/\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">20/20 Vision: How to convert 20/20 based measure to Diopters | Happy Eyesight</a></p>\n<p>tabela e distances, nga feet, ne meter: <a href=\"https://www.metric-conversions.org/length/feet-to-meters.htm\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://www.metric-conversions.org/length/feet-to-meters.htm</a></p>",
